{"tid":1171884,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳寶明苑 創新高","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T13:05:27.000Z","uid":4361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"223db3057f3ca65f5115c1e847dfee3f7b9a1f49","tid":1171884,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"鄰近港鐵站屋苑放盤向來搶手，買家遇心儀單位即拍板入市。世紀21物業(將軍澳)分行經理魏仕良表示，新近錄得將軍澳寶明苑成交，單位為B座(寶柏閣) 高層13室，實用面積426平方呎，原業主於本月初放盤，原開價450萬元，獲區內綠表買家以446.8萬元(居二市場價) 承接，累減3.2萬元或0.7%，實用面積呎價10,488元，創下屋苑同類單位新高價紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主早於2010年2月購入上述單位，當時作價約106.5萬元(未補地價)，持貨逾9年至今沽售，賬面獲利約340.3萬元，單位期內升值3.2倍。"},{"pid":"edb373b565ea6f2d99c88cc6487941d1218cb6df","tid":1171884,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"油翠都係呢個價"},{"pid":"365329b4226b351ea4936dbb7ac5e882daaab58c","tid":1171884,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"450萬樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebf763e8a61c35ba647540eb6f0f3ed2738d934","tid":1171884,"uid":122318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"居屋唔計"},{"pid":"12bddd820583166f31059de80d60401b0fffa70c","tid":1171884,"uid":29799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"廣明苑, 寶明苑好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef05226f29a6f39d6f26b5dda2c8f5b0e597e3b","tid":1171884,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12bddd820583166f31059de80d60401b0fffa70c","tid":1171884,"uid":29799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"廣明苑, 寶明苑好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"尚德勁多公屋毒癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"